(157, 2, '2018-05-23 10:34:51', '2018-05-23 10:34:51', '[caption id="attachment_158" align="alignnone" width="300"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-158" src="http://localhost/wp_news_site/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/oTgq5PTl9w-300x169.png" alt="Michelle and Barack Obama (AP Photo/Pablo Martinez Monsivais, File)" width="300" height="169" /> Michelle and Barack Obama (AP Photo/Pablo Martinez Monsivais, File)[/caption]\r\n\r\n<div class="add-to-any styky-addtoany js-sticky-header visible">\r\n<div class="container">\r\n<div id="block-addtoanybuttons" class="block block-addtoany block-addtoany-block">\r\n<div class="content">\r\n<div class="addthis_inline_share_toolbox">\r\n<div id="atstbx" class="at-resp-share-element at-style-responsive addthis-smartlayers addthis-animated at4-show" role="region"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="meta-tp-5 article-main-section2">\r\n<div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item">\r\n\r\nNetflix says that it has reached a deal with Barack and Michelle Obama to produce material for the streaming service.\r\n\r\nNetflix said Monday, in a tweet, that the former president and first lady will produce films and series for the service, potentially including scripted and unscripted series, documentaries and features.\r\n\r\n<img class="wp-image-159 alignleft" src="http://localhost/wp_news_site/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IBViZ4h9YH-300x175.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="175" />\r\n\r\nNetflix chief executive Ted Sarandos said that the Obamas are uniquely position to discover and highlight stories of people who make a difference in their communities.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\nBarack Obama recently appeared as a guest on David Letterman''s Netflix talk show.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Netflix says it has signed Barack and Michelle Obama', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'netflix-says-it-has-signed-barack-and-michelle-obama', '', '', '2018-05-23 10:34:51', '2018-05-23 10:34:51', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp_news_site/?p=157', 0, 'post', '', 0),
